<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.77seventy77.CDGPlayer</id>
  <name>CD+G Player</name>
  <summary>CD+G and CD+EG karaoke disc player</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A karaoke disc player supporting CD+G and CD+EG formats.
      Plays disc images from .cue/.bin files as well as ZIP and 7z archives.
      Supports MKV export with AV1 video and FLAC audio.
      CD+EG support based on hcs64's decoder (used with permission).
    </p>
  </description>
